cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CE, cs.CY, cs.SI

This paper involves the application of a mixture-of-experts framework to personalize sepsis treatment, which involves both deep reinforcement learning (DRL) and kernel-based reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science). Additionally, the paper involves the use of patient data, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
